properties.description: Posted by Rafael00393 Hanover Center Road, Hanover NHRolling hills along the New Hampshire countryside, with few spectators along the road, before being welcomed into the home of Dartmouth University - Hanover, where a party awaits. A late day start almost assures a very warm to hot race.

properties.description: Posted by Rafael001 East 85th Street, NY NYNo one does it better than NYC. Run the perimeter of Central Park, then meet the cheering throngs on 7th Ave down to Times Square, then sing and dance your way down 42nd Street, finally racing down the West Side Highway to Battery Park.
